  m_text: "\u201CHold this. Now, you don\u2019t have a lot of time. You need to assemble
    a ritual to fix yourself. It will need a magic circle and an incantation\u2026
    and probably some materials too. I can only do so much from out here, but I will
    help. For a favor, of course, but I have a feeling you\u2019d do what I want
    anyways, once you\u2019re safe, yourself. Now\u2026\u201D "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
